text: Oleksandra Serhiivna Gridasova (; born 5 July 1995) is a Ukrainian female rhythmic gymnast. Gridasova competed alongside London 2012 Olympians Olena Dmytrash, Yevgeniya Gomon, Valeriia Gudym, and rookie Anastasiya Voznyak at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, where she and her Ukrainian team placed seventh in the group all-around final with a total score of 34.282. ==References== == External links == * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian rhythmic gymnasts Category:Sportspeople from Kharkiv Category:Gymnasts at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Ukraine Category:Universiade medalists in gymnastics Category:European Games silver medalists for Ukraine Category:European Games bronze medalists for Ukraine Category:Universiade gold medalists for Ukraine Category:Universiade silver medalists for Ukraine Category:Medalists at the 2013 Summer Universiade Category:Medalists at the 2015 Summer Universiade
